Steve Bastoni https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Bastoni 0 Stephen Bastoni (born 20 March 1966) is an Italian Australian actor. He is best known for his role as Constable Yannis 'Angel' Angelopoulos in Police Rescue and as Steve Parker in Neighbours. Stephen_Bastoni ( born_20_March_1966 ) is an_Italian_Australian_actor .
